refactor: Enhance upload service and file repository
- Cleaned up the import statements in upload_service.go for better readability. - Improved the CleanupAbandonedUploads and CreateUploadSession methods by removing unnecessary comments and simplifying logic. - Refactored findOrCreatePath to utilize new repository methods for better clarity and efficiency. - Added FindOrCreateDirectory and FindOrCreateRootDirectory methods to the FileRepository interface for atomic directory operations. - Implemented RecursivelySoftDelete in the file repository to efficiently handle soft deletes using SQL CTE. - Updated CreateOrUpdate method to handle metadata and improve zombie record detection logic. - Enhanced error handling and logging throughout the file repository methods. - Ensured consistent naming conventions for conversion functions in the repository layer.
